{"tid":1979651,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"許智峯點解撐蘋果日報？點推動黄色經濟圈？｜","createTime":"2020-04-19T14:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T14:51:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e60963d7c372e158962e16a5e700dd089c82e10","tid":1979651,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"#黃色經濟圈 #報導有價 #撐蘋果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許智峯點解撐蘋果日報？點推動黄色經濟圈？｜<br />\n新聞自由戰線 📰📱｜峯頻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2FAj_B-Npa0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2FAj_B-Npa0&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=2435189d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2FAj_B-Npa0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許智峯<br />\n4.73K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n希望大家身體力行，支持蘋果日報繼續為公民發聲💪🏻💪🏻訂閱蘋果日報做會員：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F...&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=70eb5d97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F...&h=bbc6d9d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/...</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報沒有黨財團，屢受國家級的經濟封鎖，但仍堅持下去捍衛新聞自由。我們每一個香港人就是蘋果日報繼續營運的後盾，我在此呼籲大家，努力推動傳媒界的 #黃色經濟圈！<br />\n儘管現今有不少網媒可選擇，但多一份報導就是多一個角度，多一個真相紀錄，而且蘋果絕對是紙媒的最後防線！📰<br />\n<br />\n#報導有價 #撐蘋果 #為公民發聲 #黃色經濟圈 #港島許智峯"},{"pid":"6c1912c522732c1dfc1c0b7ea91a59cdde8dcf48","tid":1979651,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJe0vuC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJe0vuC.jpg&h=3f088870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc3c14c7159adf9c3da859d50912b706f20f9fe2","tid":1979651,"uid":36595,"li